Package edu.umn.cs.csci3081w.project.model

Class PassengerFactory

java.lang.Object
edu.umn.cs.csci3081w.project.model.PassengerFactory
public class PassengerFactory extends Object
PassengerFactory class for creating passengers in the simulation. The PassengerFactory generates passengers with randomized or deterministic names and destinations based on the current stop and last stop.
